lead_paragraph: The Brazilian crowd was one of the quietest ever for their national soccer team, but it was still not quiet enough when the ball came into the box in the 29th minute.

headline.print_headline: Paralympics: Silence for Brazil! Crowd at Blind Soccer Struggles With Quiet
